{"tid":741482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【皇天擊殺？】天價轉會引不滿 靚女主播咒 C 朗受傷","createTime":"2018-07-13T16:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T04:30:34.000Z","uid":20634,"like":6,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb634cef3ebc416fd8745402557229733dc49bd","tid":741482,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/07/13/7/7375eafe8f76f10298152e2a3e198b2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F7%2F7375eafe8f76f10298152e2a3e198b2e.jpg&h=b376ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙球王 C 朗拿度以一億歐元天價由皇家馬德里轉會至祖雲達斯，球迷們的反應兩極，有人認為他能提升祖雲達斯的實力，甚至帶領球隊衝擊歐聯，不過亦有人認為他會衝擊原有陣容和球員的發揮，不過，最令反對者不滿的，應該是他的天價轉會和人工，甚至有人詛咒他受傷。<br />\n<br />\n一向熱愛動物並關注牠們權益的意大利節目主持人 Daniela Martani 認為， C 朗拿度的轉會費太高，直言這是「恥辱」，又指一億歐元能夠令全世界的動物都獲救。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n除了轉會費外， Daniela Martani 又認為 C 朗拿度的人工太高，她指出對方擁有這輩子，甚至他的兒子和孫子都花不完的財富，對他獲得高薪感到不滿，並出言詛咒他於第一場比賽就受傷。"},{"pid":"6a41544f83a6ce120d14a03ed05a9c13203d8767","tid":741482,"uid":132587,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"你隻臭雞三萬都唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18215e7d7e68414857a60fd2184628b95d4f4446","tid":741482,"uid":13955,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通你有資格拎咩 臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bb3ae5730049726c101e725759ea64e84eb923","tid":741482,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咬你政府D老綜咩"},{"pid":"3dc8bba148a2ffb542563260c5404bcf06f760a2","tid":741482,"uid":144466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T19:52:16.000Z","msg":"佢個反朗理由勁過連登所有反朗既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma